  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to use a novel load monitoring technology to correlate limb&#xD;
      loading to ankle fracture outcomes. This study will collect continuous limb loading data and&#xD;
      will provide the first objective insight into how limb loading directs fracture healing.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
